Vusi Mthalane ON behalf of Elaine Steabler, founder of Hibiscus Animal Welfare, NPO 127787, I would like to thank the following people for the assistance and donations received for the lost and abandoned cats which our organisation is feeding, sterilising and inoculating in the Umtwenteni area - the management and staff of Abingdon Spar, management and staff of all the shops in the JTV centre, two ladies who have knitted blankets, Jack Thomson and family and countless others who have donated in many ways. If anyone could assist with food or the rehoming of any of these cats, contact Elaine on 039 681 3909 or email freeway@telkomsa.net Adrian Smith Tweni volunteer   24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.